# 📍 Day 7 — S3 & Advanced S3

## 🎯 Objective

Understand Amazon S3 and advanced storage features for durability, security, and cost optimization.

---

## 📦 Amazon S3 (Simple Storage Service)

### 📌 Key Features

* Object storage service
* Unlimited storage
* 99.999999999% durability
* Highly scalable

---

## 📂 Storage Classes

* **S3 Standard**

  * Frequently accessed data

* **S3 IA (Infrequent Access)**

  * Lower cost, less frequent usage

* **S3 Glacier**

  * Archival storage
  * Very low cost

---

## 🔁 Lifecycle Policies

* Automatically move data between storage classes
* Helps reduce storage cost

---

## 🗂️ Versioning

* Keeps multiple versions of objects
* Protects against accidental deletion

---

## 🔐 Security

* IAM Policies
* Bucket Policies
* Pre-signed URLs (temporary access)

---

## ⚖️ Key Concepts

| Feature      | Description   |
| ------------ | ------------- |
| Durability   | 99.999999999% |
| Scalability  | Unlimited     |
